      "target": {
        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "fix(agents): use CJK-aware token estimation for tool results",
        "body": "## What Problem This Solves\n`TOOL_RESULT_CHARS_PER_TOKEN = 2` 与 `estimateStringChars`的中文字符权重(4 chars/token)不匹配，导致CJK-rich内容被2倍高估，触发false token overflow错误，中断中文工作流。\n\n例如：85k中文字符被估计为170k tokens，实际应为~85k，导致本不应触发的preemptive compaction提前激活。\n\n## Evidence\n### Verifiable Behavior\n- **Issue Reference**: #95327\n- **Real Behavior Proof**: 19个token估计测试通过，包括CJK-specific测试用例\n- **Test Results**: \n```\n[pnpm test] preemptive-compaction.test.ts\nTests 19 passed (19)\nDuration 7.63s\n\nCJK Test: 85,000+ Chinese chars estimated as ~85,000 tokens (ratio: ~1.0)\nMixed Lang Test: ratio 0.8-1.5, healthy\n```\n\n### Technical Evidence\n- **Before**: `TOOL_RESULT_CHARS_PER_TOKEN = 2` 导致CJK被double-count\n- **After**: `= 4` 与正常文本估计一致\n- **Files Changed**: `src/agents/embedded-agent-runner/run/preemptive-compaction.ts` (1 line)\n- **Test Updates**: `preemptive-compaction.test.ts` added 3 CJK-specific cases\n\n### Regression Risk\n- Low: 仅修改常数值，无逻辑变更\n- 所有19个估计测试通过\n- 回归可能性：tool result token预算现在更准确，不会over-estimate\n\n## Why This Change Was Made\n使tool result token estimation与CJK字符权重对齐，防止false overflow，确保多语言工作流公平对待CJK字符。\n\n## User Impact\n- 中文工作流不再因错误的token overflow中断\n- Tool result上下文预算更准确\n- 无配置或操作变更，零用户学习成本",
